1
00:00:00,352 --> 00:00:02,373
=A Splendid Match=
(Based on A Splendid Match by Chen Xiang Hui Jin)

2
00:00:02,373 --> 00:00:04,869
(Extra Chapter)

3
00:00:13,640 --> 00:00:17,199
(The night before the enemy attacked,
I had a dream.)

4
00:00:18,320 --> 00:00:19,239
(In the dream,)

5
00:00:21,480 --> 00:00:24,199
(all these years,
I've worked well at the imperial court.)

6
00:00:24,760 --> 00:00:26,120
(I greet everyone with a smile,)

7
00:00:26,120 --> 00:00:27,760
(and never reveal my true intention,)

8
00:00:28,359 --> 00:00:29,888
(believing I never make any mistakes.)

9
00:00:30,800 --> 00:00:32,719
(But that night,
heavy rain poured down.)

10
00:00:33,479 --> 00:00:34,840
(Her eyes blurred in wine,)

11
00:00:35,600 --> 00:00:39,039
(yet she saw the blood on my hands)

12
00:00:40,200 --> 00:00:44,320
(and the side I most wanted to conceal.)

13
00:01:06,080 --> 00:01:08,608
(First meeting)

14
00:01:28,040 --> 00:01:29,159
(She's courteous)

15
00:01:29,640 --> 00:01:30,799
(and treats me politely.)

16
00:01:31,560 --> 00:01:33,400
(Rumors paint her
as spoiled and domineering.)

17
00:01:34,040 --> 00:01:35,760
(Even engagement is difficult for her.)

18
00:01:37,159 --> 00:01:39,359
(But I know that's not true.)

19
00:01:40,079 --> 00:01:41,799
(Those who grew up
without parental love)

20
00:01:42,680 --> 00:01:46,920
(can only shield themselves
from the world with thorns.)

21
00:01:48,640 --> 00:01:50,480
Greetings, Lord Yanyun.

22
00:02:02,120 --> 00:02:06,000
I never imagined Madam Ji would entrust
even Linxia Restaurant to your care.

23
00:02:07,120 --> 00:02:08,560
Grandmother dotes on me.

24
00:02:09,360 --> 00:02:11,719
Henceforth, I hope you will favor us
with your patronage.

25
00:02:14,319 --> 00:02:15,080
This way, please.

26
00:02:36,159 --> 00:02:37,240
Who sent you?

27
00:03:28,230 --> 00:03:31,680
(Two hearts as one)

28
00:03:37,568 --> 00:03:38,528
Let's go.

29
00:03:41,344 --> 00:03:46,560
- Good!
- Good!

30
00:03:47,264 --> 00:03:49,600
- Bravo!
- Bravo!

31
00:03:52,159 --> 00:03:52,759
Over here.

32
00:03:52,919 --> 00:03:54,199
Jinrong, wait for me!

33
00:03:55,680 --> 00:03:56,719
I saw many dragon dances.

34
00:03:56,879 --> 00:03:58,240
Fire-breathing dragons are rare.

35
00:03:58,360 --> 00:03:59,439
My Lord, be careful!

36
00:03:59,616 --> 00:04:01,344
It's fine. Let's find another spot.

37
00:04:01,344 --> 00:04:02,360
Look!

38
00:04:02,360 --> 00:04:03,719
I was telling someone earlier.

39
00:04:03,919 --> 00:04:06,120
The New Year here
isn't as lively as in Tongzhou.

40
00:04:06,120 --> 00:04:08,159
It seems I was speaking too boldly.

41
00:04:08,599 --> 00:04:10,159
I think you are right.

42
00:04:10,439 --> 00:04:12,280
The capital is livelier though,

43
00:04:12,759 --> 00:04:14,080
there's no molten iron firework.

44
00:04:14,879 --> 00:04:15,960
Tongzhou is better.

45
00:04:19,879 --> 00:04:22,120
They say walking over
three bridges cures all ailments.

46
00:04:22,439 --> 00:04:23,519
Let's go do that too.

47
00:04:35,560 --> 00:04:36,279
- Good!
- Good!

48
00:04:36,279 --> 00:04:37,639
- Good!
- Good!

49
00:04:37,800 --> 00:04:40,319
My lady, look!
That lantern is exquisite.

50
00:04:42,439 --> 00:04:43,480
Let's go take a look.

51
00:04:51,240 --> 00:04:52,199
My Lord, look.

52
00:04:53,680 --> 00:04:54,800
Which one set that up?

53
00:04:55,000 --> 00:04:56,040
Such extravagance.

54
00:04:56,839 --> 00:04:57,720
Let's go see.

55
00:05:00,839 --> 00:05:02,480
Make way, please.

56
00:05:04,199 --> 00:05:05,000
Lady Gu!

57
00:05:05,439 --> 00:05:06,480
- Lady Gu!
- Xiangyun.

58
00:05:06,879 --> 00:05:08,199
Madam Nie, you're here too?

59
00:05:08,839 --> 00:05:10,199
Happy New Year, Lady Gu.

60
00:05:10,519 --> 00:05:11,720
Happy New Year, Madam Nie.

61
00:05:12,240 --> 00:05:13,480
Happy New Year, Lady Qingpu.

62
00:05:13,600 --> 00:05:14,639
Happy New Year.

63
00:05:14,879 --> 00:05:16,279
Lady Gu, Happy New Year.

64
00:05:16,759 --> 00:05:18,000
Xiangyun, Happy New Year.

65
00:05:18,680 --> 00:05:19,839
How come you look so lovely?

66
00:05:20,199 --> 00:05:21,360
Are you wearing new clothes?

67
00:05:21,680 --> 00:05:23,759
Yes, my mother made them for me.

68
00:05:25,639 --> 00:05:28,079
Madam Nie, how have you been lately?

69
00:05:28,680 --> 00:05:30,639
Yes, we're all settled now.

70
00:05:30,959 --> 00:05:33,000
Steward Lv treats us kindly.

71
00:05:33,199 --> 00:05:34,959
He takes good care of us both.

72
00:05:35,560 --> 00:05:37,879
Those Nie family people
haven't come to us again.

73
00:05:38,199 --> 00:05:39,639
All thanks to you.

74
00:05:40,000 --> 00:05:41,959
That's good then. I'm relieved.

75
00:05:44,600 --> 00:05:45,759
Everyone!

76
00:05:47,720 --> 00:05:48,759
On this New Year occasion,

77
00:05:49,800 --> 00:05:52,639
our master specially
erected this lantern tower

78
00:05:53,000 --> 00:05:55,120
as a festive celebration.

79
00:05:55,920 --> 00:05:58,040
We invite you to play the verse game.

80
00:05:58,879 --> 00:06:02,439
From the first to the fifteenth day,
nightly prizes await.

81
00:06:03,240 --> 00:06:04,319
Tonight's prize

82
00:06:04,879 --> 00:06:08,480
is this Eight-treasure Glazed Lantern
atop the tower.

83
00:06:10,600 --> 00:06:12,079
So beautiful.

84
00:06:12,680 --> 00:06:14,920
This lantern's value
lies not in its cost,

85
00:06:15,480 --> 00:06:16,639
but in its symbolism.

86
00:06:17,560 --> 00:06:20,800
Should anyone win this treasure,

87
00:06:21,680 --> 00:06:24,480
it brings fortune and joy
to his household.

88
00:06:25,240 --> 00:06:27,839
All wishes shall be fulfilled.

89
00:06:31,519 --> 00:06:32,600
I'd like to try.

90
00:06:34,519 --> 00:06:35,399
Me too.

91
00:06:36,079 --> 00:06:37,759
Both, please come to the stage.

92
00:06:41,024 --> 00:06:45,439
Mother, I want
that Eight-treasure Glazed Lantern.

93
00:06:45,439 --> 00:06:47,759
But I don't know verse games.

94
00:06:49,399 --> 00:06:52,319
In past temple fairs,
her father brought her.

95
00:06:52,639 --> 00:06:54,528
Whether solving riddles
or playing verse games,

96
00:06:54,528 --> 00:06:57,160
he always won her many prizes.

97
00:06:57,519 --> 00:07:00,519
This time, she wants
to win prizes again.

98
00:07:02,519 --> 00:07:05,439
Xiangyun, do you like that lantern?

99
00:07:07,399 --> 00:07:09,279
I'll win it for you, okay?

100
00:07:09,720 --> 00:07:10,439
Yes!

101
00:07:12,279 --> 00:07:13,920
Lady Gu, you excel at drinking games?

102
00:07:14,199 --> 00:07:14,839
Of course.

103
00:07:15,000 --> 00:07:17,680
Be it number-guessing, verse games,

104
00:07:17,680 --> 00:07:19,072
arrow-shooting, or horse-riding,

105
00:07:19,072 --> 00:07:21,079
my lady excels at all games,

106
00:07:21,360 --> 00:07:22,399
always winning.

107
00:07:22,519 --> 00:07:23,160
Right, my lady?

108
00:07:23,399 --> 00:07:24,439
But that was in Tongzhou.

109
00:07:24,600 --> 00:07:26,680
They say the capital
has all kinds of talents.

110
00:07:26,800 --> 00:07:27,839
I dare not talk big.

111
00:07:28,720 --> 00:07:29,879
Are you happy?

112
00:07:37,360 --> 00:07:38,639
I'd like to try.

113
00:07:39,600 --> 00:07:41,000
What a brave girl!

114
00:07:41,399 --> 00:07:42,920
- Good!
- Good!

115
00:07:42,920 --> 00:07:45,759
Lord Yanyun, that seems to be Lady Gu.

116
00:07:48,160 --> 00:07:49,199
There are six people.

117
00:07:49,720 --> 00:07:50,759
It won't be easy to win.

118
00:07:50,959 --> 00:07:52,120
Anyone?

119
00:07:53,360 --> 00:07:54,000
Here.

120
00:08:04,480 --> 00:08:06,680
Why are you wearing a mask?

121
00:08:07,079 --> 00:08:09,160
I bear a scar on my face
and prefer not to show it.

122
00:08:09,680 --> 00:08:10,839
Does it affect the game?

123
00:08:11,560 --> 00:08:12,600
No, not at all.

124
00:08:12,879 --> 00:08:14,800
As long as you feel good. Please.

125
00:08:20,240 --> 00:08:22,279
Before we begin the game,
let's state the rules.

126
00:08:22,560 --> 00:08:23,600
I'll be the game master.

127
00:08:24,079 --> 00:08:25,560
This row has six lanterns.

128
00:08:26,160 --> 00:08:26,879
For eight rounds.

129
00:08:28,399 --> 00:08:29,639
Dice decides the assignment.

130
00:08:30,160 --> 00:08:31,720
The number rolled on the dice

131
00:08:32,360 --> 00:08:33,879
refers to the corresponding lantern.

132
00:08:35,639 --> 00:08:38,559
If there are no objections,
then we shall begin.

133
00:08:44,000 --> 00:08:44,720
Six.

134
00:08:50,149 --> 00:08:52,120
(Fragrance)

135
00:08:52,120 --> 00:08:52,879
Fragrance.

136
00:08:57,279 --> 00:08:59,000
The Spring landscape is beautiful,

137
00:08:59,840 --> 00:09:02,176
and the breeze brings
the fragrance of flowers and grass.

138
00:09:02,840 --> 00:09:04,480
From afar, I know it's not snow,

139
00:09:04,720 --> 00:09:06,559
but a hidden fragrance arrives.

140
00:09:07,639 --> 00:09:09,799
Scattered, turned to mud,
ground to dust,

141
00:09:10,200 --> 00:09:11,919
only its fragrance remains as before.

142
00:09:12,919 --> 00:09:14,919
Sparse shadows slant
across shallow, clear water,

143
00:09:15,120 --> 00:09:17,360
and a hidden fragrance drifts
beneath the dusky moon.

144
00:09:17,559 --> 00:09:19,240
The plum blossom isn't as white as snow,

145
00:09:19,559 --> 00:09:21,279
but its fragrance beats snow's.

146
00:09:21,919 --> 00:09:23,968
Fine wine from Lanling,
with fragrance like tulips,

147
00:09:23,968 --> 00:09:26,159
held in jade bowls, glowing like amber.

148
00:09:26,600 --> 00:09:29,120
Amid the fragrance of rice blossoms,
talk of a good year.

149
00:09:29,120 --> 00:09:30,399
All around, the sound of frogs.

150
00:09:30,919 --> 00:09:33,759
- Good!
- Good!

151
00:09:35,600 --> 00:09:37,799
Sunlight on the fragrance censer
kindles violet mists.

152
00:09:38,240 --> 00:09:40,759
From afar, I see a waterfall
hanging over the river.

153
00:09:41,200 --> 00:09:43,559
Rather die holding fragrance
on the branch,

154
00:09:43,559 --> 00:09:45,919
than be blown down by the north wind.

155
00:09:46,879 --> 00:09:48,519
The fragrant mist
dampens her cloudy hair,

156
00:09:48,759 --> 00:09:50,720
the clear moonlight
chills her jade-white arms.

157
00:09:50,879 --> 00:09:54,240
- Good!
- Good!

158
00:09:55,320 --> 00:09:56,600
Fragrance fills my sleeves,

159
00:09:56,600 --> 00:09:57,919
but the distance separates us.

160
00:09:59,320 --> 00:10:00,960
The lilac fragrance remains,

161
00:10:01,279 --> 00:10:03,120
pouring out sorrows
to the spring breeze.

162
00:10:07,759 --> 00:10:08,320
Got it...

163
00:10:08,320 --> 00:10:09,840
You may pass this round,

164
00:10:09,840 --> 00:10:10,879
but not the next.

165
00:10:11,279 --> 00:10:12,399
Admit defeat now,

166
00:10:12,600 --> 00:10:15,039
and you can get five taels of silver
from my maid.

167
00:10:25,960 --> 00:10:27,000
I admit defeat.

168
00:10:36,200 --> 00:10:37,279
If you admit defeat,

169
00:10:37,279 --> 00:10:39,559
you can get five taels of silver
from my maid.

170
00:10:46,360 --> 00:10:47,279
I admit defeat.

171
00:10:48,600 --> 00:10:49,639
Another one down.

172
00:10:50,000 --> 00:10:51,039
How many are left?

173
00:10:51,039 --> 00:10:52,080
There are still five.

174
00:10:52,600 --> 00:10:54,000
Well, more rounds to go.

175
00:10:54,440 --> 00:10:57,759
(She's employing
so many tricks just for a prize.)

176
00:10:58,080 --> 00:10:59,639
(It's utterly fascinating.)

177
00:11:00,840 --> 00:11:03,519
(Yeah, she's adorable and amusing.)

178
00:11:04,159 --> 00:11:05,759
(To put it plainly, she's simple.)

179
00:11:06,399 --> 00:11:11,120
(With such a temperament, if no one
protects her, what will she do?)

180
00:11:11,120 --> 00:11:13,840
(Yeah, pitiful, yet fascinating.)

181
00:11:13,840 --> 00:11:15,200
Only two people remain.

182
00:11:15,399 --> 00:11:17,240
It's truly quite tense.

183
00:11:17,399 --> 00:11:18,639
This young lady is remarkable!

184
00:11:19,039 --> 00:11:20,399
She fought her way to the end.

185
00:11:20,840 --> 00:11:23,039
Lord Guan is great too,
answering fluently.

186
00:11:23,039 --> 00:11:24,120
- He's not losing ground.
- Lord Guan.

187
00:11:24,240 --> 00:11:25,840
- Now a good show begins.
- If you admit defeat now,

188
00:11:26,000 --> 00:11:28,200
you can get ten taels of silver
from my maid.

189
00:11:29,440 --> 00:11:30,200
No way.

190
00:11:32,360 --> 00:11:33,080
Twenty taels.

191
00:11:33,480 --> 00:11:34,279
No.

192
00:11:34,679 --> 00:11:35,559
Thirty taels.

193
00:11:42,720 --> 00:11:44,879
It's still 'Fragrance'. Please go on.

194
00:11:45,600 --> 00:11:47,584
People gather in Spring,
fireworks fill the air,

195
00:11:47,584 --> 00:11:50,784
sober up from wine at midnight,
and the fragrance of orchids fills the room.

196
00:11:53,279 --> 00:11:54,919
Crystal beads swayed gently
in the breeze,

197
00:11:54,919 --> 00:11:57,344
and the courtyard filled
with the fragrance of roses.

198
00:11:57,344 --> 00:11:59,200
One night, a pure fragrance blooms,

199
00:11:59,559 --> 00:12:01,240
spreading spring
across ten thousand miles.

200
00:12:01,840 --> 00:12:03,399
The east wind ripples the sublime glow,

201
00:12:03,759 --> 00:12:05,728
and fragrant mist shrouds
as the moon shines.

202
00:12:06,360 --> 00:12:07,759
Lotus breezes carry the fragrance,

203
00:12:08,639 --> 00:12:10,399
and bamboo dew drips with a clear sound.

204
00:12:16,639 --> 00:12:18,399
It seems the young lady will lose.

205
00:12:18,480 --> 00:12:20,159
This lantern will
likely go to Lord Guan.

206
00:12:20,720 --> 00:12:23,919
What a pity. The young lady
was just one step away.

207
00:12:24,679 --> 00:12:27,200
Young lady, you still have time.

208
00:12:29,799 --> 00:12:33,240
Lady Gu.

209
00:12:39,639 --> 00:12:40,200
Got it!

210
00:12:40,480 --> 00:12:41,960
Flowers will die, do what one may.

211
00:12:42,480 --> 00:12:44,000
The returning swallow seemed familiar.

212
00:12:44,240 --> 00:12:45,799
Alone, I wander the fragrant path.

213
00:12:46,600 --> 00:12:51,320
- Good!
- Good!

214
00:12:55,799 --> 00:12:57,480
My lady, what quick wit you have!

215
00:12:58,360 --> 00:13:00,559
I admit defeat.

216
00:13:01,960 --> 00:13:03,840
It was this young lady
who won the prize.

217
00:13:03,960 --> 00:13:05,759
Incredible! Astonishing!

218
00:13:06,600 --> 00:13:09,320
- Good!
- Good!

219
00:13:10,360 --> 00:13:11,840
- Good!
- Good!

220
00:13:11,840 --> 00:13:12,679
- Xiangyun.
- Lady Gu.

221
00:13:18,720 --> 00:13:20,799
- Good!
- Good!

222
00:13:23,639 --> 00:13:24,440
Remarkable!

223
00:13:25,679 --> 00:13:26,639
- Good!
- Good!

224
00:13:28,960 --> 00:13:30,240
Thank you, Lady Gu.

225
00:13:31,240 --> 00:13:33,000
Thank you for today.

226
00:13:33,720 --> 00:13:36,416
We live at the embroidery workshop,
so we can't stay out for long.

227
00:13:36,559 --> 00:13:37,679
We must take our leave now.

228
00:13:42,120 --> 00:13:43,480
Return and get rest.

229
00:13:45,320 --> 00:13:46,360
Let's go, Xiangyun.

230
00:13:46,679 --> 00:13:47,519
Off we go!

231
00:13:47,519 --> 00:13:48,480
Here, let me carry it.

232
00:13:49,679 --> 00:13:50,840
Alright, be careful.

233
00:13:53,440 --> 00:13:55,080
Fortunately, Lord Guan surrendered.

234
00:13:55,399 --> 00:13:57,600
I was so nervous
that my palms were sweating.

235
00:13:59,360 --> 00:14:00,480
Lord Guan was something.

236
00:14:00,759 --> 00:14:02,240
He wouldn't even accept your silver.

237
00:14:04,080 --> 00:14:06,600
I keep feeling he resembles someone.

238
00:14:07,320 --> 00:14:08,080
Who is it?

239
00:14:10,320 --> 00:14:11,399
I must be mistaken.

240
00:14:11,679 --> 00:14:14,039
That person probably
wouldn't come play this.

241
00:14:22,759 --> 00:14:23,799
Molten iron fireworks!

242
00:14:24,960 --> 00:14:25,460
Look!

243
00:14:25,460 --> 00:14:25,960
Here!

244
00:14:25,960 --> 00:14:27,000
Let's go. This way.

245
00:14:29,720 --> 00:14:30,519
Good!

246
00:14:31,600 --> 00:14:32,639
Another one!

247
00:14:36,759 --> 00:14:37,840
There's more!

248
00:14:46,120 --> 00:14:48,799
- Long live Yan!
- Long live Yan!

249
00:14:49,360 --> 00:14:52,159
- Long live Yan!
- Long live Yan!

250
00:14:52,759 --> 00:14:55,720
- Long live Yan!
- Long live Yan!

251
00:14:56,120 --> 00:14:59,080
- Long live Yan!
- Long live Yan!

252
00:14:59,559 --> 00:15:02,559
- Long live Yan!
- Long live Yan!

253
00:15:03,120 --> 00:15:06,120
- Long live Yan!
- Long live Yan!

254
00:15:06,600 --> 00:15:09,600
- Long live Yan!
- Long live Yan!

255
00:15:10,039 --> 00:15:13,039
- Long live Yan!
- Long live Yan!

256
00:15:13,480 --> 00:15:15,080
(She's laughing so happily.)

257
00:15:15,879 --> 00:15:17,720
(I love seeing her smile like this.)

258
00:15:18,799 --> 00:15:20,360
(I want to protect her always.)

259
00:15:22,039 --> 00:15:24,080
(I finally understand
what I truly want.)

260
00:15:27,080 --> 00:15:29,200
(Heart stirs with joy)

261
00:15:29,200 --> 00:15:32,559
(After everything,
I've returned to this battlefield.)

262
00:15:33,919 --> 00:15:35,440
(But this time is different.)

263
00:15:36,679 --> 00:15:38,120
(I never imagined)

264
00:15:38,759 --> 00:15:41,080
(she'd abandon everything to find me.)

265
00:15:49,472 --> 00:15:51,682
♪Once I painted seasons with my brush♪

266
00:15:51,905 --> 00:15:55,612
♪But fell through time's vast fissure♪

267
00:15:57,169 --> 00:15:59,186
♪Strength or mildness,
both turned bitter brew♪

268
00:15:59,359 --> 00:16:03,529
♪Each longing thought
brings endless rue♪

269
00:16:05,088 --> 00:16:07,099
♪I've seen right and wrong pass through♪

270
00:16:07,209 --> 00:16:11,040
♪Old vows turned to ash,
waters flow east anew♪

271
00:16:11,424 --> 00:16:16,480
♪Gentle closeness means
understanding your heart's freedom♪

272
00:16:16,480 --> 00:16:17,759
- (When I think of all the injustice)
- Lord Yanyun.

273
00:16:17,759 --> 00:16:19,720
- (she endured,)
- What took you so long?

274
00:16:20,000 --> 00:16:21,519
(all those risks she took,)

275
00:16:21,879 --> 00:16:23,879
(and all the hardships she suffered,)

276
00:16:24,039 --> 00:16:25,879
(I was so heartbroken,)

277
00:16:26,720 --> 00:16:28,480
(so guilty,)

278
00:16:29,440 --> 00:16:33,639
(and so joyful like I'm mad.)

279
00:16:35,399 --> 00:16:38,840
(Jinzhao, this is all my fault.)

280
00:16:42,157 --> 00:16:49,585
♪Filling every crease with yesterday♪

281
00:17:06,978 --> 00:17:09,131
♪Once shared cups
while speaking of debts and grudges♪

282
00:17:09,645 --> 00:17:13,484
♪But tumbled into
the deep ravine of rumors♪

283
00:17:14,829 --> 00:17:16,912
♪Partings and reunions
both moved like chess pieces♪

284
00:17:16,912 --> 00:17:20,688
♪Every heartfelt word turned false♪

285
00:17:22,401 --> 00:17:24,657
♪I've seen the sun and moon
pass through♪

286
00:17:24,864 --> 00:17:28,523
♪Sighing light and shadow
sail no more together♪

287
00:17:29,012 --> 00:17:36,235
♪One wrong choice
turned old friends to gulls adrift♪

288
00:17:36,341 --> 00:17:39,840
♪With every step away, I glance anew♪

289
00:17:39,996 --> 00:17:43,542
♪My thoughts grow cold as rust♪

290
00:17:43,931 --> 00:17:47,542
♪The starry river sees you journey far♪

291
00:17:48,759 --> 00:17:49,440
What's wrong?

292
00:17:49,720 --> 00:17:50,359
Nothing.

293
00:17:50,599 --> 00:17:51,440
I had a dream.

294
00:17:53,800 --> 00:17:54,800
What did you dream about?

295
00:17:55,319 --> 00:17:57,720
That you never came, and I died here.

296
00:17:59,230 --> 00:18:05,160
♪Filling every crease with yesterday♪

297
00:18:05,160 --> 00:18:07,720
(No need to mention
what happened later.)

298
00:18:08,480 --> 00:18:10,480
(Half-drunk is when
the fun really kicks in.)

299
00:18:10,480 --> 00:18:11,680
(At near drunkenness,)

300
00:18:12,039 --> 00:18:13,160
(one is in high spirits.)

301
00:18:13,960 --> 00:18:15,000
(One cup left unfinished,)

302
00:18:15,000 --> 00:18:16,799
(yet many more await.)

303
00:18:17,839 --> 00:18:21,960
(Stories should end
at just the right moment.)
